Description:
    Generates a social sharing component to display various social media share buttons. It can be
    used for either a page or a specific component.

Available share options
    - Facebook:     :facebook
    - Google Plus:  :google
    - Twitter:      :twitter
    - Xing          :xing
    - linkedin      :linkedin
    
Example:
    Render default: Current page url and all share options:
      = render_cell(:share, :show, '')

    Render current page url and specific share options:
      = render_cell(:share, :show, '', [:google, :twitter, :linkedin]

    Render specific url and specific share options:
      = render_cell(:share, :show, '', [:facebook, :google, :twitter]